data.description: Welcome Home to this 4-bedroom, 3-bath two-story property on Lake Brittany in Bella Vista. With a private dock, 2 levels of living space & 2 large decks, this home is perfect for entertaining & enjoying all that lake life has to offer. The primary suite is on the main level. The lower level currently serves as a lucrative Airbnb suite, complete with kitchenette, 1 bedroom/1 full bath, a dining area & large entertaining space. The air-conditioned workshop on the lower level is a craftsman's dream. There's potential to convert shop & storage to add'l living space.  This property combines the charm of lakeside living with income-generating potential. Custom cabinets throughout.  The 3-car garage has room for your side by side, boat or 3rd car. As a Bella Vista resident, you'll enjoy access to all that Bella Vista has to offer ... golf courses, clubhouses, restaurants, marinas and world class mountain bike trails, all designed to enhance your quality of life.
